    <h1>Zero-Click Search</h1>
    <p class="description">A search query where the user gets a sufficient answer <strong>directly on the SERP</strong> and never clicks through to a website. Approximately 58-65% of all Google searches result in zero clicks — a growing challenge for SEO-driven businesses.</p>
